'''瑞銀集團'''（{{Lang-en|'''UBS Group AG'''}}）{{efn|1=瑞銀集團的英文名“{{lang|en|UBS}}”源自其前身之一的“{{Link-en|瑞士联合银行|Union Bank of Switzerland}}（{{lang|en|'''U'''nion '''B'''ank of '''S'''witzerland}}）”首字母縮寫。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/profiles/companies/UBS:SW-ubs-union-bank-of-switzerland|title=UBS: Union Bank of Switzerland|last=|first=|date=|website=Bloomberg|language=en|access-date=2018-06-16}}</ref> 儘管“瑞士聯合銀行”已於1998年被併購，但其名稱縮寫依舊被用作併購后機構的法律和商業名稱。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ubs.com/global/en/about_ubs/investor_relations/faq/about.html|title=UBS Corporate Information: What does 'UBS' stand for?|last=|first=|date=|website=www.ubs.com|language=en|access-date=2018-06-16|quote=The name 'UBS' came from one of our predecessor firms - the Union Bank of Switzerland. However, just like other prominent brands which used to be an abbreviation of a company name, UBS is no longer considered an acronym.}}</ref> 在1998年的併購過程中，時任瑞銀董事長{{Link-en|馬塞爾·奧斯佩爾|Marcel Ospel}}打算繼續用“瑞士聯合銀行”這個名稱稱呼新公司，但在收購美國券商{{Link-en|普惠投資公司|Paine Webber}}的時候則改用了“瑞銀（{{lang|en|UBS}}）”。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ubs-ospel/ubs-architect-ospel-leaves-battered-bank-idUSL2279145320080423|title=UBS architect Ospel leaves battered bank|last=O'Donnell|first=John|date=2008-04-28|work=Reuters|access-date=2018-08-08|language=en-US|quote=The three-times married banker was the architect of what was originally meant to be called United Bank of Switzerland — the fusion of Swiss Bank Corporation and Union Bank of Switzerland in 1998. He later masterminded the acquisition of U.S.-based PaineWebber.}}</ref> 至1998年11月，新公司用名被確認為“瑞銀（{{lang|en|UBS}}）”或“瑞銀集團（{{lang|en|UBS Group AG}}）”；而其相關衍生公司則通常被命名為“瑞銀投資銀行（{{lang|en|UBS Investment Bank}}）”、“瑞銀金融服務（{{lang|en|UBS Financial Services}}）”和“瑞銀資產管理（{{lang|en|UBS Asset Management}}）”等。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ubs.com/global/en/about_ubs/about_us/ubs_group/group.html|title=UBS Organizational Structure: How we are organized|last=|first=|date=|website=www.ubs.com|language=en|access-date=2018-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180808202805/https://www.ubs.com/global/en/about_ubs/about_us/ubs_group/group.html|archive-date=2018-08-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 對應的中文名源自其[https://www.ubs.com/cn/sc.html 官方中文網站]。}}是一家在[[瑞士|瑞士]]成立的[[跨國公司|跨國]][[投资银行|投資銀行]]和[[金融服務|金融服務]]公司。瑞銀集團的總部有兩處，分別位於[[瑞士|瑞士]]的[[蘇黎世|蘇黎世]]和[[巴塞爾|巴塞爾]]；而作為全球最大的[[世界最大银行列表|瑞士銀行機構]]，瑞銀集團在全球各大金融中心城市都設有办公机构。瑞銀集團以其对客户资料的嚴格保密政策和銀行保密文化而著稱。{{efn|1=瑞銀集團在其財富管理、[[投資銀行|投資銀行]]、資產管理和[[私人銀行|私人銀行]]業務方面執行全球{{Link-en|客戶保密|Client confidentiality}}標準。在瑞士，瑞銀的業務受到《{{Link-en|瑞士聯邦銀行法|Federal Act on Banks and Savings Banks}}》的監督，該法案禁止銀行依據某些條款或條件向第三方披露客戶資料。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-swiss-banking-secrecy-exclusive/exclusive-swiss-prosecutors-seek-widening-of-secrecy-law-to-bankers-abroad-idUSKBN1D01CI|title=Exclusive: Swiss prosecutors seek widening of secrecy law to...|last=Neghaiwi|first=Brenna Hughes|date=2017-10-31|work=Reuters|access-date=2018-06-16|language=en-US}}</ref> 而在瑞士境外，瑞銀集團遵循所在國對銀行保密和客戶隱私的相關法規。而在其第三大市場的[[美國|美國]]，瑞銀集團遵守{{Link-en|美國金融業監管局|Financial Industry Regulatory Authority}}的保密條款。即除了某些條款或條件下，禁止未經授權的分發客戶資料。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.finra.org/industry/customer-information-protection|title=FINRA.org: Customer Information Protection|last=|first=|date=|website=www.finra.org|language=en|access-date=2018-06-22}}</ref> 無論各國法律法規有何不同，瑞銀集團都規定了其對其所有業務的保密政策均有自由裁量權。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://money.howstuffworks.com/personal-finance/banking/swiss-bank-account1.htm|title=How Swiss Bank Accounts Work|last=Obringer|first=Lee Ann|date=2007-11-06|work=HowStuffWorks|access-date=2018-04-05|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://europa.eu/rapid/press-release_IP-15-5043_en.htm|title=Fighting tax evasion: EU and Switzerland sign historic tax transparency agreement|last=Moscovici|first=Pierre|date=2015-05-27|website=europa.eu|publisher=European Commission|language=en|access-date=2018-04-05|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.